extends layout

block content

    section(class='legal-info')

        h2(class='legal-subtitle') Consent 
        p By accessing and using the Downtown Donuts website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website. Your continued use of the site following any changes to these terms will be deemed your acceptance of those changes.

        h2(class='legal-subtitle') Collection of Personal Information 
        p Downtown Donuts collects personally identifiable information such as your name, email address, phone number, and any comments or messages you submit through our website. We also collect anonymous demographic information such as your ZIP code, age, and general preferences. Additionally, information about your computer hardware and software may be automatically collected, including your IP address, browser type, domain names, and access times. This information is used to operate our service and maintain its quality.

        h2(class='legal-subtitle') Use of Personal Information
        p Downtown Donuts uses your personal information solely to operate our website and deliver the services you have requested. We may also use your information to inform you of new products, services, or promotions that may be of interest to you. We do not sell, rent, or lease your personal information to third parties. We may share data with trusted partners to help us perform statistical analysis, send email communications, or provide customer support. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information except to provide these services to Downtown Donuts

        h2(class='legal-subtitle') Security of Personal Information  
        p Downtown Donuts is committed to securing your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. We store all personally identifiable information on computer servers in a controlled and secure environment. When personal information is transmitted to other websites or services, it is protected through the use of industry standard encryption protocols such as Secure Socket Layer (SSL). However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        h2(class='legal-subtitle') Cookies 
        p The Downtown Donuts website uses cookies to help personalize your online experience. A cookie is a small text file placed on your hard disk by a web page server. Cookies cannot be used to run programs or deliver viruses to your computer and are uniquely assigned to you. They help us remember your preferences and improve your overall experience on our site. You have the ability to accept or decline cookies through your browser settings. Please note that declining cookies may limit your ability to use certain features of our website.

        h2(class='legal-subtitle') Children Protection 
        p The Downtown Donuts website is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately at the email below or call us.

        h2(class='legal-subtitle') Changes to Statement    
        p Downtown Donuts reserves the right to update or modify these Terms of Use at any time without prior notice. We encourage you to review this page periodically to stay informed of any changes. Your continued use of the Downtown Donuts website following the posting of any changes constitutes your acceptance of those changes. If you have any questions or concerns regarding these terms please contact us at the email down below.



